cast.overview: Abandoned by her father, a young woman embarks on a thousand-mile odyssey through the backroads of America where she meets a disenfranchised drifter. But despite their best efforts, all roads lead back to their terrifying pasts and to a final stand that will determine whether their love can survive their otherness.
cast.title: Bones and All

details.biography: Hannah is an actor & filmmaker from Sydney. After graduating the prestigious National Institute of Dramatic Art, Hannah was a finalist for the Heath Ledger Scholarship. FOR NOW, Hannah’s first feature as writer/director, was nominated for best picture at multiple film festivals and was distributed worldwide in 2019.
details.name: Hannah Barlow
